OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain
OL,6,Fclearing many areas this evening
OL,7,Fthough likely persisting through to
OL,8,Fdawn across southeast England and
OL,9,Fnorthern Scotland. Clear spells
OL,10,Ffollowing from the west, with a few
OL,11,Fshowers, possibly heavy across western
OL,12,FScotland. Milder than previous nights.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSunday:FRain persisting across
OL,15,Fnorthern Scotland, otherwise sunny
OL,16,Fspells and scattered showers on
OL,17,FSunday. Showers heaviest and most
OL,18,Ffrequent across the west. Temperatures
OL,19,Fstill a little below average for mid-
OL,20,FMay.
